{"tid":848590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杜特爾特指自己或患癌 稱如果到了第三期會放棄治療","createTime":"2018-10-05T04:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T05:35:20.000Z","uid":41404,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6a43da01f0633b2c669de5665f9208ca1eb3ef","tid":848590,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】菲律賓總統杜特爾特透露可能患上癌症，正等待健康檢查結果。<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特周四出席活動發表演說時透露自己可能患病，他指在三星期前曾接受內窺鏡及結腸鏡檢查，診斷消化道和結腸是否出現異常。醫生日前要求他再做多次檢查確認，正等候報告。<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特表示，不清楚自己的身體狀況，但就指萬一確診癌症，他會對外公布病情。又稱如果已到了第三期，他會選擇放棄治療，亦不會再擔任總統。<br />\n<br />\n一向言論出位的杜特爾特過去一周沒有公開露面，更缺席周四的內閣會議和取消另一項活動。外界猜測他健康出問題。當局否認，指73歲的杜特爾特只是因為疲倦需要休息。不過他於同日晚上證實自己可能患病。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=322608&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D322608%26refer%3Dshare&d=%2FrE3f8HXw7%2BNXC4UwzoGVi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=6b986c4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D322608%26refer%3Dshare&h=0724bb08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=322608&amp;refer=share</a>"},{"pid":"34a8f7517c3626fc77d61dc7229a638e6edc3d6b","tid":848590,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f0793c9e8b15d6d610c4a68c63c97dcf0dce08","tid":848590,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5d6a43da01f0633b2c669de5665f9208ca1eb3ef","tid":848590,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】菲律賓總統杜特爾特透露可能患上癌症，正等